title: Thrane Wynarn
text: Thrane Wynarn was the second-oldest child of King [[Galifar I|Galifar Wynarn]]. When the Kingdom of [[Galifar]] was formed, the king granted Thrane the role of governor-prince over the domain of [[Daskara]], the area later known as [[Thrane]]. He governed this province until his death in 22 YK, when he led an army to stop the rampaging [[dragon]] [[Sarmondelaryx]].
